Implement the API to manage addresses, including:

* DTOs
* Repository
* Service
* Controller
* Unit tests

API endpoints:

* GET /addresses 200 - List all addresses
* GET /addresses/:id 200 - Get address by id
* POST /addresses 201 - Create address
* PUT /addresses/:id 200 - Update address
* DELETE /addresses/:id 204 - Delete address

General guidelines:
* Use AuthUtils to get the logged in user
* Use existing implementations as reference for naming and organization conventions

